00:05:30.910 --> 00:05:31.910
Haley?

00:05:31.910 --> 00:05:37.110
Wait, please.

00:05:37.110 --> 00:05:39.629
I don't know what's happening.

00:05:39.629 --> 00:05:41.949
Did you talk to Emily about my posts?

00:05:41.949 --> 00:05:42.949
Yes, we do.

00:05:42.949 --> 00:05:44.949
Do you gossiped about me?

00:05:44.949 --> 00:05:47.550
No, why would I look up to you?

00:05:47.550 --> 00:05:51.790
You're supposed to be the mature one and you're just like Emily busy running your

00:05:51.829 --> 00:05:53.829
Haley.

00:05:53.829 --> 00:05:57.430
Look, I can see you're upset.

00:05:57.430 --> 00:06:04.560
But trust me, this is a huge misunderstanding.

00:06:04.560 --> 00:06:06.160
I love you.

00:06:06.160 --> 00:06:11.199
I would never, ever say anything behind your back.

00:06:11.199 --> 00:06:19.699
